{
  "text": "Reconstructed PET images are analyzed with a pipeline developed by CATI. A standard uptake value ratio (SUVR) with a threshold of 0.7918 has been used to categorize our population as Ab positive or Ab negative according to a method previously described [CITATION_1] .",
